#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid ""
"A delicate blend of soft pink roses and baby's breath, perfect for "
"expressing love and gratitude."
msgstr ""
"Een delicate mix van zachtroze rozen en gipskruid, perfect om liefde en "
"dankbaarheid uit te drukken."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Aline Turner, Bouquet Designer"
msgstr "Aline Turner, boeketontwerper"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Aline is the mastermind behind our bespoke floral arrangements."
msgstr "Aline is het brein achter onze bloemstukken op maat."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_kickoff
msgid "Bloom with Joy:"
msgstr "Bloei met vreugde:"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid "Blushing Harmony"
msgstr "Blozende harmonie"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_image_text_overlap
msgid ""
"Brighten any corner of the globe with our express 24-hour worldwide flower "
"delivery service."
msgstr ""
"Verlicht elke hoek van de wereld met onze express 24-uurs wereldwijde "
"bloemenbezorgservice."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_freegrid
msgid "Bringing the Beauty of Nature to Your Space"
msgstr "Breng de schoonheid van de natuur naar je kamer"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid "Celebrate with Our Best-Selling Bouquets, perfect for every occasion."
msgstr ""
"Vier feest met onze best verkochte boeketten, perfect voor elke gelegenheid."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid "Discover Our Most Loved Arrangements"
msgstr "Ontdek onze meest geliefde arrangementen"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_orchid.field_theme_utils__display_name
msgid "Display Name"
msgstr "Schermnaam"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid "Elegant Simplicity"
msgstr "Elegante eenvoud"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_freegrid
msgid ""
"Enhance your surroundings with our exquisite floral arrangements and garden "
"designs. We offer a variety of options that bring the serenity and beauty of "
"nature into your home or workspace."
msgstr ""
"Verfraai je omgeving met onze prachtige bloemstukken en tuinontwerpen. We "
"bieden een verscheidenheid aan opties die de sereniteit en schoonheid van de "
"natuur in je huis of werkruimte brengen."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_freegrid
msgid "Explore Our Gardens"
msgstr "Ontdek onze tuinen"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_title
msgid ""
"Explore our handcrafted floral arrangements, each meticulously designed to "
"convey beauty, elegance, and a touch of nature's artistry."
msgstr ""
"Ontdek onze handgemaakte bloemstukken, stuk voor stuk zorgvuldig ontworpen "
"om schoonheid, elegantie en een vleugje kunstzinnigheid uit de natuur over "
"te brengen."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_kickoff
msgid "Fresh Flowers Delivered to Your Doorstep!"
msgstr "Verse bloemen thuisbezorgd!"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_image_text_overlap
msgid "Global 24-Hour Flower Delivery"
msgstr "Wereldwijde 24-uurs bloemenlevering"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_orchid.field_theme_utils__id
msgid "ID"
msgstr "ID"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Iris Joe, Customer Relations"
msgstr "Iris Joe, Klantrelaties"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Iris ensures that each customer has a delightful experience."
msgstr "Iris zorgt ervoor dat elke klant een heerlijke ervaring heeft."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid ""
"Light pink blossoms with golden leaves, bringing a touch of springtime charm "
"to any space."
msgstr ""
"Lichtroze bloesems met goudkleurige bladeren die elke ruimte een vleugje "
"lente charme geven."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Meet the Team"
msgstr "Maak kennis met het team"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Mich Stark, Operations Manager"
msgstr "Mich Stark, Operations Manager"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Mich makes sure everything runs smoothly."
msgstr "Mich zorgt ervoor dat alles soepel verloopt."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid ""
"Minimalist white florals in a sleek vase, embodying sophistication and grace."
msgstr ""
"Minimalistische witte bloemen in een strakke vaas, die verfijning en gratie "
"belichamen."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_title
msgid "Our Creations"
msgstr "Onze creaties"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid "Petal Poetry"
msgstr "Bloemblaadjes Poëzie"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid "Sunset Serenade"
msgstr "Serenade bij zonsondergang"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_orchid.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "Thematools"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Tony Fred, Floral Director"
msgstr "Tony Fred, bloemendirecteur"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Tony leads the creative vision for the shop."
msgstr "Tony leidt de creatieve visie voor de winkel."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid ""
"Vibrant hues of orange and red capture the warmth and beauty of a summer "
"evening."
msgstr ""
"Levendige oranje en rode tinten geven de warmte en schoonheid van een "
"zomeravond weer."
